<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Excerpted from </em><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781469677248" class="external" target="_blank">Gun Country: Gun Capitalism, Culture, and Control in Cold War America</a> <em>by Andrew C. McKevitt. Copyright © 2024 by Andrew C. McKevitt. Reprinted by permission of University of North Carolina Press.</em></p>
</span>
									
																		
